      <title>上诉法院批准对美国大选的投注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/betting-on-us-elections-get-fresh-greenlight-from-appeals-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国 11 月大选投票前五周，美国上诉法院为大量投注奠定了基础，如今美国人可以再次合法地对国会选举进行下注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/betting-on-us-elections-get-fresh-greenlight-from-appeals-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 15:10:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称纽约市长亚当斯可能因腐败案面临更多指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/nyc-mayor-adams-may-face-more-counts-in-corruption-case-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[检察官表示，纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 可能因其腐败案而受到进一步指控，并补充称“很有可能”还有其他被告也被点名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/nyc-mayor-adams-may-face-more-counts-in-corruption-case-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 14:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业市场数据强劲，美联储押注受压，美国国债下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/treasuries-slide-as-resilient-job-market-data-weighs-on-fed-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国企业上个月增加的就业岗位多于预期，美国国债价格下跌，这向关注劳动力市场以寻找美联储需要大幅降息迹象的交易员发出了混合信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/treasuries-slide-as-resilient-job-market-data-weighs-on-fed-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:40:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济信心飙升 南非首席执行官看到复苏迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/south-african-ceos-see-green-shoots-as-economic-mood-improves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非一些最大公司的首席执行官表示，自联合政府成立以来，在强劲的投资者情绪的推动下，南非开始看到复苏的迹象，但南非需要谨慎避免自满。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/south-african-ceos-see-green-shoots-as-economic-mood-improves</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:40:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港券商陷入“百年不遇”的股市狂潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hong-kong-brokers-swamped-by-once-in-a-century-stock-frenzy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港的股票经纪人正经历职业生涯中最忙碌的时期之一，一位拥有 31 年经验的资深人士将香港股市的突然上涨描述为“百年不遇”的事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hong-kong-brokers-swamped-by-once-in-a-century-stock-frenzy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:09:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗袭击事件后避险购买减少，黄金回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/gold-holds-near-record-as-mideast-escalation-stokes-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商等待以色列对伊朗导弹袭击的回应，黄金价格下跌，抹去了周二的部分涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/gold-holds-near-record-as-mideast-escalation-stokes-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 23:02:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列誓言对伊朗袭击进行报复，油价继续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗发射了约 200 枚弹道导弹，以色列誓言要对其进行报复，这加大了该地区原油供应的风险，油价延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 22:51:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
